EffectiveSource
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Numerical code for the effective source for a point particle moving in a
curved background spacetime

Getting the code
----------------
To get the code, run

git clone git://github.com/barrywardell/EffectiveSource

Compiling
---------
This code has no requirements other than a C compiler.

Usage
-----
The code parameters for the geodesic are currently hardcoded
into the main function in main.cc. There are no command line
arguments available.

Changelog
---------
31 Jan 2012	Initial version made public

